%F A029337 a(n) = floor((n^3+39*n^2+258*n+9747)/8640 - (n mod 2)*n/64 + ((n^3+2*n^2+2*n+1) mod 4)*n/32 + ((3*n^3+2*n^2+4*n+1) mod 5)/5 - (((n+3) mod 4) + 3*(n mod 4))*7/64). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Apr 21 2026
